, “Diding Headwater Forest Nature Preserve (formerly known as Jing Xi County Provincial Nature Reserve), Jing Xi County, 
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF6D6AD2F7A997701752BA74" box="[2133,2386,297,326]" country="China" name="Guangxi" pageId="150" pageNumber="911">Guangxi Zhuang</collectingRegion>
Autonomous Region, 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF6D6AD2F7B7971216A1BA5E" box="[2123,2209,331,364]" name="China" pageId="150" pageNumber="911">China</collectingCountry>
. 
<geoCoordinate id="A1A05039FF6D6AD2F74A97121757BA5E" box="[2230,2391,331,364]" degrees="23" direction="north" minutes="07" orientation="latitude" pageId="150" pageNumber="911" precision="55555" seconds="12" value="12.0">23°07 12°N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="A1A05039FF6D6AD2F69297121419BA5E" box="[2414,2585,331,364]" degrees="105" direction="east" minutes="57" orientation="longitude" pageId="150" pageNumber="911" precision="925" value="57.6">105°57°36'E</geoCoordinate>
, elevation 
<quantity id="036C9B1BFF6D6AD2F7A5972A16AEBAA6" box="[2137,2222,371,404]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.78" pageId="150" pageNumber="911" unit="m" value="978.0">978 m</quantity>
above sea level.”
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF6D6AD2F82D97C617CCB900" pageId="150" pageNumber="911" type="discussion">
Limited genetic data suggestit is sister to a clade that includes 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF6D6AD2F6FB97931766BAD1" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1891" box="[2311,2406,458,483]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Harpiocephalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="150" pageNumber="911" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="feae">M. feae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF6D6AD2F6879793141BBAD1" box="[2427,2587,458,483]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="150" pageNumber="911" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="beelzebub">M. beelzebub</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF6D6AD2F82E97AB1696B939" box="[2002,2198,498,523]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="150" pageNumber="911" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="annamitica">M. annamitica</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF6D6AD2F75097AB1748B939" box="[2220,2376,498,523]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="150" pageNumber="911" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="walstoni">M. walstoni</taxonomicName>
, M. swilla, and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF6D6AD2F82E944C1646B900" authorityName="Goodwin" authorityYear="1958" box="[2002,2118,533,562]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Rhogeessa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="150" pageNumber="915" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="aenea">M. aenea</taxonomicName>
. Two subspecies recognized.
</subSubSection>
</paragraph>
