— Ngoc Linh Nature Reserve in SC 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF6D6AD2F8BC948F19BAB9C5" box="[1856,1978,726,759]" name="Vietnam" pageId="150" pageNumber="911">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
